07:53.595 --> 07:56.604
Do you mean do I understand
the science of genetic engineering?

07:56.764 --> 08:00.007
I mean, do you understand
why you were genetically engineered?

08:00.127 --> 08:00.942
Yes.

08:01.965 --> 08:02.965
My mother,

08:03.718 --> 08:07.518
- along with Mr. Olivier Roth...
- Who committed suicide in 2008.

08:08.582 --> 08:11.247
... wanted to ensure
a generation of empathetic human beings.

08:11.367 --> 08:12.753
In 2008,

08:12.873 --> 08:15.030
