08:31.550 --> 08:34.750
Your parents managed
to stay in hiding for some time,

08:35.070 --> 08:38.270
largely due to the help
of Carlton Riddlemeyer, is that correct?

08:38.909 --> 08:39.856
Yes.

08:44.603 --> 08:47.812
Carlton Riddlemeyer retired
from the position of Under Secretary

08:47.932 --> 08:51.855
