in 2009 after a failed Senate bid.

08:51.975 --> 08:55.163
What can you tell us
about Carlton Riddlemeyer?

08:56.846 --> 08:58.291
Honestly, not much.

08:58.837 --> 09:00.459
I never really knew him.

09:00.619 --> 09:03.568
