09:06.226 --> 09:07.820
And your father?

09:08.519 --> 09:10.769
He was fine. He took me to Toronto.

09:11.679 --> 09:15.183
I was home schooled and kept pretty much
out of the spotlight.

09:15.462 --> 09:17.762
My father was very protective of me,

09:18.238 --> 09:20.396
