09:20.556 --> 09:22.857
And when you were 18, what did you do?

09:28.808 --> 09:31.464
Mr. Riddlemeyer along with Mr. Roth

09:31.970 --> 09:33.726
had established a trust

09:34.240 --> 09:36.822
that I had access to when I was 18.

09:37.046 --> 09:38.210
You founded

09:38.330 --> 09:41.259
