09:41.379 --> 09:42.752
with that money,

09:42.872 --> 09:46.797
which recently the press has referred to
as "ground zero".

09:50.775 --> 09:52.025
That's correct.

09:58.117 --> 10:01.558
18 years ago, the first human clone,

10:01.678 --> 10:03.134
Robert Melnikov Junior,

10:03.254 --> 10:05.615
was born into this world with a gift.

10:05.735 --> 10:07.447
A gift for mankind.

10:07.723 --> 10:09.581
The gift of empathy.

10:10.321 --> 10:13.482
Now, the Robert Melnikov Junior
Fertility Center

10:13.985 --> 10:15.660
can offer an evolutionary breakthrough:

10:16.282 --> 10:18.871
the awakening of your Jacobson's organ.

10:19.032 --> 10:20.051
Simply put,

10:20.940 --> 10:24.883
this gland located here,
at the base of the nasal cavity

10:25.492 --> 10:27.672
can help us understand one another.

10:28.022 --> 10:30.772
Empathy is the gift of knowledge,

10:31.175 --> 10:33.552
understanding and compassion.

10:33.956 --> 10:36.953
That infomercial ran in 178 countries
in 45 languages including Estonian...

10:37.073 --> 10:40.705
Your fertility center
was entirely devoted

10:40.825 --> 10:44.348
to the sales and distribution
of your sperm

10:44.611 --> 10:48.109
to hundreds and thousands of women
throughout the world.

10:51.090 --> 10:53.490
