11:10.661 --> 11:11.655
Well yes...

11:11.969 --> 11:12.675
no.

11:14.084 --> 11:15.610
I mean it was business,

11:16.038 --> 11:18.517
but I wanted to carry out
my parents' desire

11:19.064 --> 11:20.858
to make the world a better place.

11:20.978 --> 11:23.493
Did you run extensive tests
on your sperm?

11:24.174 --> 11:26.217
