36:36.215 --> 36:39.617
the CTLV virus of 2022

36:40.067 --> 36:43.454
that killed 13 million people,

36:44.380 --> 36:45.786
to the descendents

36:46.117 --> 36:48.000
of the Melnikov experiment.

36:50.121 --> 36:54.220
The Cambium cell epidemic,
from 2025 to 2027,

36:54.340 --> 36:57.546
took 22 million lives.

36:58.015 --> 37:00.183
- It too came from...
- Alright stop it.

37:00.303 --> 37:03.160
... Robert Melnikov Jr.

37:05.553 --> 37:08.104
The HIV-4 strain outbreak

37:08.264 --> 37:11.164
of 2034, six million dead.

37:11.284 --> 37:12.535
I said: Stop it!

37:15.973 --> 37:17.543
We faced those pandemics

37:18.703 --> 37:20.741
and we dealt with them,
we learnt from them.

37:20.901 --> 37:22.219
At what cost?

37:27.165 --> 37:30.047
We are not here to dispute the facts.

37:32.157 --> 37:34.422
The question is: What is to be done

37:34.582 --> 37:36.868
- with the children?
- Dr. Sandström.

37:38.625 --> 37:42.315
This inquiry was called
after a classified document,

37:42.435 --> 37:46.453
written in conjunction with
the Consortium of the Unified Nations,

37:47.094 --> 37:48.378
questioned whether

37:48.498 --> 37:51.467
the current direction
of the scientific community

37:51.587 --> 37:53.718
is aggressive enough.

37:54.101 --> 37:55.902
That's just fucking bullshit!

37:56.391 --> 37:59.105
There are over 150 labs
all around the world

37:59.225 --> 38:01.324
currently picking apart
those retroviruses,

38:01.484 --> 38:05.930
finding out how they reproduce
in the human body, how they stay alive!

38:06.050 --> 38:08.526
Well isn't that just
a waste of time and money?

38:08.646 --> 38:09.654
You have to know

38:09.896 --> 38:13.461
how something lives before
you can understand how it will die.

38:13.621 --> 38:15.912
And in the three months
since you began this work,

38:16.032 --> 38:18.426
how close are you to a solution?

38:18.918 --> 38:20.885
It could be right around the corner

38:21.199 --> 38:22.929
or it could be halfway to heaven.

38:23.346 --> 38:25.784
But we learn something new everyday.

38:26.300 --> 38:29.944
And do you agree that everyday
there are still these...

38:30.064 --> 38:33.108
these viral factories
walking amongst us.

38:33.228 --> 38:34.504
Quarantining

38:35.020 --> 38:38.957
3.2 million children
under the age of 18 is...

38:40.270 --> 38:42.191
challenging, yes.

38:42.718 --> 38:44.575
But I have met some of these kids.

38:45.554 --> 38:47.054
They are empathic.

38:47.476 --> 38:49.163
And they know where's at stake.

38:49.323 --> 38:53.084
No, we haven't got them all contained,
we need more money, more facilities.

38:53.244 --> 38:55.568
And so far, 4 trillion euros

38:55.908 --> 38:58.648
- has been spent on this program.
- And by the time this is over,

38:58.768 --> 39:00.596
we'll probably need another 4 trillion.

39:03.293 --> 39:06.508
The Consortium has recommended
an alternative approach.

39:06.628 --> 39:08.918
The Consortium
are a bunch of bureaucrats

39:09.038 --> 39:11.727
who should stick
to political science, not biological.

39:12.487 --> 39:14.981
The Consortium is recommending a humane

39:15.745 --> 39:19.167
eradication program
of the Melnikov lineage.

39:21.065 --> 39:22.237
That's insane.

39:23.479 --> 39:26.313
They recommend that
the program take effect immediately,

39:26.433 --> 39:28.869
and that the remains
be properly incinerated

39:29.029 --> 39:31.272
for the protection
of the general population.

39:36.408 --> 39:37.308
Hope...

39:39.821 --> 39:41.340
Those human beings,

39:43.252 --> 39:45.108
they've contracted a condition

39:46.271 --> 39:47.730
not of their own doing

39:47.850 --> 39:50.377
and you are willing
to turn your backs on them

39:50.705 --> 39:53.540
rather than allow us
the chance to find a solution.

39:53.660 --> 39:54.478
No,

39:54.638 --> 39:57.102
the recommendation
is meant to save the lives

39:57.222 --> 40:00.879
of 7 billion people
living on this planet.

40:01.309 --> 40:02.413
And you think...

40:02.773 --> 40:06.946
You think they'll be safe
if the Melnikov lineage is wiped out?

40:07.400 --> 40:11.461
Why risk a definitive solution
for the hope of a cure?

40:11.697 --> 40:13.602
Because that's how we'll endure!

40:14.255 --> 40:16.417
By solving our problems,
not running away.

40:17.856 --> 40:21.115
Because by learning
how to stop the Melnikov viruses,

40:21.425 --> 40:24.175
we may just learn
how to stop the last virus.

40:24.704 --> 40:26.144
The "last virus"?

40:29.252 --> 40:30.236
Someday,

40:31.520 --> 40:34.820
a virus could evolve
to be so perfectly efficient

40:36.392 --> 40:39.607
that it will destroy
every living thing on this planet.

40:41.720 --> 40:42.656
The end.

40:43.820 --> 40:45.380
The end of our species.

40:46.772 --> 40:48.272
The end of everything.

40:50.636 --> 40:52.292
And it's going to happen.

40:53.228 --> 40:55.952
No matter
how many corpses you throw in the fire.

40:56.072 --> 40:58.748
No matter
whether you're prepared or not.

41:02.383 --> 41:04.047
Science makes mistakes.

41:05.899 --> 41:07.586
But science is a journey.

41:08.055 --> 41:10.164
The road is long and with every step,

41:11.125 --> 41:12.812
we learn a little bit more.

41:14.385 --> 41:15.226
So,

41:16.070 --> 41:19.750
you want us
to just put our trust in science.

41:23.101 --> 41:24.906
I want you to believe in it.

41:27.109 --> 41:28.797
I want you to ask yourself:

41:30.180 --> 41:31.890
Have we gone far enough?

41:33.578 --> 41:36.226
And if you find
that the answer is "yes",

41:37.844 --> 41:38.687
fine.

41:40.164 --> 41:41.064
You stop.

41:42.883 --> 41:44.477
But don't ask me to stop.

41:44.777 --> 41:46.670
I can't see the end of the road.

41:47.983 --> 41:49.970
And if you just let me keep going,

41:51.283 --> 41:53.177
as far as I can, I promise,

41:54.302 --> 41:57.434
I will prove to you
that there is nothing to be afraid of.

41:57.827 --> 41:59.402
That it's just shadows.

41:59.722 --> 42:01.208
That 3.2 million people

42:01.328 --> 42:04.348
do not have to die
because of fear and ignorance.

42:04.468 --> 42:07.802
And that what has happened here today
need never happen again.

42:11.618 --> 42:13.235
Thank you, Dr. Sandström.

42:51.357 --> 42:52.654
You think he's dead?

42:52.936 --> 42:53.920
I dunno.

43:05.738 --> 43:06.770
He's dead.

43:07.637 --> 43:10.216
Holy shit. I've never seen a dead guy.

43:10.520 --> 43:11.504
