43:12.169 --> 43:13.309
What do we do?

43:16.930 --> 43:18.057
Did you see that?

43:20.481 --> 43:21.769
You okay, Mister?

43:24.583 --> 43:25.825
You're bleeding.

43:28.895 --> 43:29.718
Bob?

